          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">MedTech Corp - Achieved HIPAA compliance in 90 days with zero audit findings</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 text-sm">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white rounded-full">HIPAA Compliant</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white rounded-full">Zero Findings</span>
          </div>
        </div>
